cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.MM, cs.HC 

This paper deals with the mobile advertising and tracking ecosystem, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as it involves privacy concerns and potential risks to user data. It also involves data analysis and machine learning techniques (cs.SI), as well as human-computer interaction (cs.HC) as it deals with user understanding and transparency. Additionally, it touches upon cybercrime (cs.CY) as it discusses the potential misuse of user data, and multimedia (cs.MM) as it involves tracking through various forms of media such as images and videos.
